headline: Stock Market Today: Indexes Mixed; Coherent Hits 3 Sell Signals But New IPO Bullish Jumps 10%; 3 Growth Stocks Set Up Entries
summary: In the stock market today, the Dow Jones index trimmed losses made after a PPI inflation report. Coherent plunged on earnings. Bullish rose 10%.
